data.description: NEW LISTING!  Home features 2 master bedrooms with in-suite full bathrooms plus upstairs office nook. Open layout between living room, dining room and kitchen. Huge kitchen island. Prime, exterior spot in complex near park with street parking directly out front. Attached garage plus nearby assigned spot. Nice front patio plus large balcony. Large side by side upstairs laundry. Upgrades include wood flooring, high end kitchen with white cabinets, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, tankless water heater, water purifier/soft water system. Complex features resort style amenities with pool, spa, gym, BBQ, and playground. Close to the Otay Ranch Mall. Property is close to beaches, entertainment, shopping, restaurants, schools, movie theaters, freeways, and parks. Short drive to downtown San Diego & airport.  Amazing opportunity!
